      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">節南山.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>昊天不傭，降此鞠訩。昊天不惠，降此大戾。
君子如屆，俾民心闋。君子如夷，惡怒是違。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Great Heaven, unjust,
Is sending down these exhausting disorders.
Great Heaven, unkind,
Is sending down these great miseries.
Let superior men come (into office),
And that would bring rest to the people's hearts.
Let superior men execute ​their justice,
And the animosities and angers would disappear.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__006__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">xiaoya-jienanshan-001</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">poem</prop>
