      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">節南山.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>不弔昊天，亂靡有定。式月斯生，俾民不寧。
憂心如酲，誰秉國成？不自為政，卒勞百姓。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>O unpitying great Heaven,
There is no end to the disorder!
With every month it continues to grow,
So that the people have no repose.
I am as if intoxicated with the grief of my heart.
Who holds the ordering of the kingdom?
He attends not himself to the government,
And the result is toil and pain to the people.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__007__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
