      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·001.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">節南山.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>昊天不平，我王不寧。不懲其心，覆怨其正。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>From great Heaven is the injustice,
And our king has no repose.
(Yet) he will not correct his heart,
And goes on to resent endeavours to rectify him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-001__010__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
