      <prop type="x-translation-ref">節南山.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>家父作誦，以究王訩。式訛爾心，以畜萬邦。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I, Kiâ-fû, have made this poem,
To lay bare the king's disorders.
If you would but change your heart,
Then would the myriad regions be nourished.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
